window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Sometimes the path to the truth is littered with lies.</p> <p>If someone had told me that I'd find a haven among monsters, I'd have laughed in their face. But I've learned to expect the unexpected.</p> <p>Now, with the world's fate hanging in the balance, it's time to take a leap of faith. Faith in myself.</p> <p>It means leaving Shem, the watchers, and Bastian behind. It means walking into Michael's arms and trusting that he'll keep me alive long enough for me to complete my mission.</p> <p>Because the third relic piece is hidden in the enemy camp, and I'm the only one who can get to it.</p> <p>The Golden City awaits. It's time to put my acting skills to the test. It's time to lie.</p> <p>Contains mature themes.</p>"; 
